{
  "code": "006_TUBA013D",
  "route": "006",
  "locale": "cn",
  "title": "楠木翼\\N处女失去～吻",
  "beats": [
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "……我们来到了翼的房间。",
        "如果我们是普通的恋人，来到她的房间后会营造氛围。",
        "",
        "但是，没有必要做那些事情。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#背景・翼の部屋（夕）",
        "file": "BG09_02_00"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她的脸变得通红，好像中暑了一样。",
        "然后，她用迷醉的眼神凝视着我。",
        "受到了施加的『暗示』，她完全处于发情状态。",
        "",
        "刚认识时，甚至还误以为她是个男孩子。",
        "但现在的翼，完全是个女人。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「喜欢你，翼」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_001",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_001.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊！喔喔……喜欢！",
        "我也，非常喜欢你……啊啊……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她鼻子发酸，发出妖媚的声音。",
        "当然，我知道那并不是真正的『恋心』。",
        "",
        "但我并不在意。",
        "只要你能成为我的俘虏，作为一个女孩子就好了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「嘿，翼……既然我们已经成为恋人了，可以亲吻吗？」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_002",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_002.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呀！嗯，嗯，可以亲吻的！",
        "我们是情侣了呢……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她现在应该无法拒绝吧。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「当然，如果翼不喜欢的话，我不会勉强的。",
        "因为我爱你，所以想要亲吻你。」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "故意说出那种让她焦虑的话。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_003",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_003.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「不，不讨厌……想，想要亲吻！",
        "因为我也非常喜欢你，所以想要亲吻！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「这么想和我亲吻？」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_004",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_004.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「是，是的，呼啊啊……我，我想要亲吻！",
        "因为我们是情侣嘛……想要亲吻啦……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "每进行一次对话，翼的眼角就会垂下来。",
        "微微张开的嘴唇湿润而诱人。",
        "翼的身体摇晃着，甜蜜的香气扑鼻而来。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_005",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_005.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「我喜欢你……嗯呐……所以，所以……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "我轻轻地把手放在她的肩上，点了点头。",
        "从她湿润的眼眸中透出热情，让人无法移开目光。",
        "再这样拖延下去，我都忍不住了。",
        "就这样慢慢地靠近她的脸。",
        "作为信号，我们的嘴唇相互贴合在一起。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_006",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_006.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呐……啾，啾……嗯嗯，啾啾」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她的嘴唇依旧是最柔软的。",
        "就像棉花糖一样松软，心里不禁感到甜蜜。",
        "",
        "不知何时，她闭上了眼睛。",
        "这应该是翼心中期待的亲吻表情吧。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_007",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_007.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啾噗……嗯嗯，嗯嗯……啾，嗯嗯」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "就这样重复几次，接触后再分开。",
        "为了确认触感，翼微微动了动唇。",
        "",
        "她的举止如此可爱，让我不由得心跳加速。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_008",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_008.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呐，呼啊……亲了，呢……我的，",
        "初吻……啊呀」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "翼离开我的脸，发出热烈的呼吸。",
        "她带着真心幸福的笑容，感慨万分地",
        "说着话。",
        "当然她只是忘记了而已，其实并不是第一次",
        "接吻。",
        "即便如此，在有意识的翼看来，这就是",
        "初吻。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_009",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_009.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「接吻，好厉害……胸中暖洋洋的……嗯呐，",
        "幸福……这种幸福的感觉，第一次……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "翼露出笑容。",
        "从接吻带来的兴奋和让翼说出这样的话",
        "的成就感。",
        "胸中涌动着澎湃的情感，身体不由自主地动了起来。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「翼，再来一次吗？」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_010",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_010.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呀！嗯，嗯，想要更多！",
        "恋人之间的接吻，多多……嗯嗯！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "于是我们再次不知何时贴上了嘴唇。",
        "翼再次闭上眼睛，放松身体接受着吻。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・切なげ見つめ・引き",
        "file": "EV055_01"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_011",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_011.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呼……啾，嗯啾……嗯嗯，啾噜噜」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "比刚才稍微激烈一点。",
        "唇不断接触，分离，反复循环。",
        "将唇紧密贴合，这次轻轻地左右晃动头部。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_012",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_012.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呼啊！嗯嗯，啾……啾，啾布，",
        "嗯呼，嗯呣呣……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "像擦拭唇间一样，享受着那柔软的触感。",
        "",
        "那触感实在是太舒服了。",
        "翼也从那边微微颤动着唇。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_013",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_013.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯，嗯呼……啾，嗯啾……嗯呼，",
        "啾，嗯呼呼……啾呐，呣呼……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "果然，在接吻时还不习惯用鼻子呼吸吧。",
        "",
        "稍微有些不适，翼的鼻息变得粗重。",
        "微微吹拂在脸上的呼吸声，让我感到一阵阵颤抖。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・目閉じキス・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_03"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_014",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_014.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呼啊，嗯嗯……哈啊……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "然后，翼分开嘴唇，发表了感想。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_015",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_015.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呼啊，哈啊，不知为何亲吻总是有点痒痒的。",
        "但是，这真的是一种非常舒服的感觉呢」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她陶醉地微笑着，真的很有魅力。",
        "不过，这种亲吻只是个开始。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「下次试试成人之吻吧，让我们来尝试一下」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_016",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_016.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「那个，就是那种……舌头纠缠在一起的吻？",
        "虽然在电影里看过，但还没有亲身体验过……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "我知道她当然不会拒绝这个提议。",
        "但我故意说出来，想看到她扭动呻吟的样子。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「嗯，我想和心爱的翼深深地，性感地亲吻一次」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_017",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_017.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呀！嗯，嗯，来吧……我也很喜欢",
        "所以，嗯嗯……让我们来个性感的亲吻！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "听到她答应了，我重新扶住了翼的肩膀。",
        "然后，我把舌尖伸进她微微张开的嘴里。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・うっとり・引き",
        "file": "EV055_02"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_018",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_018.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯啊……！啊，嗯嗯……好舒服……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "紧紧贴合着唇，我慢慢舔着翼的口腔。",
        "",
        "用舌尖轻轻划过，翼的身体不断颤抖着。",
        "",
        "真是可爱的反应啊。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_019",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_019.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯……亲，嗯嗯……嗯呼，嗯嗯，",
        "亲亲，嗯呢……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "就这样在她的口腔里，用舌头大幅度地转动。",
        "像舔遍整个口腔一样，混合唾液在一起。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_020",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_020.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「吸吮，呼啊……嗯嗯，啊，呼啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "翼的唾液黏稠而甜美。",
        "只是稍微品尝一下，头脑就仿佛要溶化了。",
        "她的口腔温度适宜，感觉非常舒适。",
        "包裹着的柔软感也让人欲罢不能。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_021",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_021.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「亲亲……嗯呢，嗯……啊，嗯啊……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "包括许多'暗示'在内，她也开始在吻中感受到了。",
        "",
        "翼的呼吸声变得更加粗重。",
        "在亲吻声中不时掺杂着喘息声，我也越来越兴奋。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_022",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_022.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯哈啊……成人之吻，好厉害……嗯啊，",
        "口腔里好像要融化了……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "稍微分开一下嘴唇，她陶醉地呢喃道。",
        "看来，她似乎也喜欢成人之吻。",
        "她一边身体扭动着，一边说出这样的感想。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_023",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_023.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊，嗯……！更多，更多地想要，",
        "更舒服的吻，更多……呼啊……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "当然，我也是希望如此的。",
        "但是，这可是难得的留念初吻。",
        "如果只是我一个人主动的话，就太可惜了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「那么，翼你也用舌头回应一下吧，这样",
        "应该会更舒服的哦。」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_024",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_024.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯，嗯……那样肯定很舒服呢。",
        "我也会努力回应你的舌头的」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "刚刚还直视着我的嘴唇，她突然",
        "把脸凑了过来。",
        "然后开始缠绵地交织舌头。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・驚き唇半開き・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_025",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_025.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯吧……嗯呼，嗯，嗯呢……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "对她来说，应该是初吻，但她的主动",
        "非常强烈。",
        "她的身体已经觉醒为女人，",
        "渴望着快乐。",
        "仿佛在模仿我刚才的动作，舌头相互",
        "摩擦在一起。",
        "舌尖柔软地在口腔中游动着。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_026",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_026.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呼，啾……嗯吭，啾噜……吭噗，",
        "嗯呼……嗯哩嗯呼……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "当然，我也不会忘记主动动舌头。",
        "舌尖相互碰撞，在我们之间打转。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_027",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_027.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呼，嗯嗯，啾吭……嗯呼，嗯哩哦！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "就这样，擦拭着舌头的每一个部位。",
        "我们随心所欲地动着舌头，",
        "下一刺激无法预料。",
        "这种感觉变成了快感，从脊椎传来",
        "一阵阵的刺激。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_028",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_028.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啾吭……嗯呼，哩哦……吭噗，",
        "嗯呼……啾吭，嗯呼……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "舌头黏黏地在口腔中打转，吮吸着唾液。",
        "这也是刚才我做的动作。",
        "反过来，我也将唾液送入她的口腔。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_029",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_029.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯！ 啾吭噗噜，吭噗，啾吭呼！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她瞬间睁大了眼睛，但没有抵抗。",
        "毫不犹豫地，将那口唾液吞下去。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_030",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_030.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯吱，嗯嗯，啾吧，喽呢……嗯嘿！",
        "我的也喝掉！嗯嗯，嗯吱！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "舌头缠绕着互相交融的唾液。",
        "甜蜜而迷人，翼的味道。",
        "湿湿的淫荡唾液声音回响着，",
        "头脑似乎要糊涂了。",
        "不知不觉间，我们的嘴巴都湿湿的。",
        "即使如此，我们还是继续深吻。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_031",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_031.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呼！太棒了，好舒服，",
        "啾吧，喽呢，嗯呼呼……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "亲吻的快感真是相当不错啊。",
        "她的眼神完全迷离，脸颊也红透了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_032",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_032.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呼，嗯嗯，啾吧……嗯呼，嗯吱！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "",
        "夹杂在亲吻间的喘息声也相当诱人。",
        "火热的身体扭动不已。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
        "file": "EV055_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_TUBA_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_tuba_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_006_TUBA013D_033",
        "file": "voice/tuba_006_tuba013D_033.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啾吧，喽喽喽呢……啾吧噜！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV055・蕩け舌絡め・アップ",
